By Samuel Ajayi (Sundiata Post) For calling Nasir el-Rufai “Mr. Bulldozer”, Buhari has told anyone who cares to listen that he is aware of most of, if not all, the things his aides and supporters are doing. Calling el-Rufai that name also showed he supported his (el-Rufai) action on the demolition of the building in question; either rightly or wrongly. Thirdly, he has shown where he stands in the crisis rocking the Kaduna APC chapter. So all you crier-than-the-bereaved and apostles of “Buhari is not aware” now you know. Your man might be playing the saint, he is not one. Except in your warped estimation… Source: Facebook